@puckzer

In terms of killing Subaru because of how he smells, he's the single exception in the ReZero World where he isn't a witch cultist but has that smell, and an exception that hasn't existed in that world for more than a few days by the time Rem Killed him, in other words, it was literally just common sense that he was a witch cultist that was just hiding it (even though we as readers/watchers know it's wrong because we are outsiders) and we all know how witch cultists are

For the other parts, meh I'm either neutral or just respect that you have your opinions based on which part you're talking about, it's just the smell part that was objectively wrong
